<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1059,774,825]" pageId="2" pageNumber="685">
B e s c h r e i b u n g: Die Art ist habituell mit 
<taxonomicName authority="MORAWITZ, 1870" authorityName="MORAWITZ" authorityYear="1870" box="[682,1059,774,796]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Nomada" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="685" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mutabilis">
